bt settings module for paroli

This is a very rough start for a bt module for paroli settings.

this should reside in either of:

when running from source folder:
 [wherever you put the source on your phone]/paroli-services/

or when using an installed paroli

  /usr/share/paroli/services/

if oyu have any questions join #paroli on freenode and ask mirko-paroli/vegyraupe or pop a mail to vegyraupe@paroli-project.org